name: Siamese Cat
description:
Watercolour and ink painting on quality watercolour paper of a beautiful Siamese cat with piercing bright blue eyes, surrounded by mocha browns and cream background.
Wax texture to add interest. My prints are mounted with cream board. My beautiful handmade cards can be sent directly to a friend or loved one, just let me know what to write in the card.
For more information contact Sarah Scragg
